               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Malkǝʾa gubaʾe “Collection of Images” (fols.1ra-50vb)&#xD;
- Tǝmḫǝrtä ḫǝbuʾat “Teaching of Mysteries” (fols. 1ra-4vb)  &#xD;
- Malkǝʾa Māryām “Image of Mary” (incipit fol. 12ra) (ChRep 347, no. 327)&#xD;
- Malkǝʾa Māryām “Image of Mary” (incipit fol. 16va), unidentified.&#xD;
- Malkǝʾa Māryām “Image of Mary” (incipit fol. 18v) (ChRep 339, no. 213)&#xD;
- Malkǝʾa Māryām “Image of Mary” (fols. 20va-24vb, 7va-vb, 7ra-rb, 6ra-6vb, 25ra-vb) (ChRep 343, no. 268)&#xD;
- Malkǝʾa Iyäsus “Image of Jesus” (fols. 26ra-vb, 29ra-vb, 27ra-vb, 30ra-vb, 28va-vb, 28ra-rb, 31ra-vb, 33ra-vb)&#xD;
- Malkǝʾa Iyäsus “Image of Jesus” (incipit fol. 32ra) (ChRep 199, no. 125)&#xD;
- Malkǝʾa Yoḥannǝs Mäṭmǝq “Image of John the Baptist” (fols. 38ra-41vb) (ChRep 340, no. 227)&#xD;
- Malkǝʾa Giyorgis “Image of George” (fols. 45ra-50vb) (ChRep 200, no. 147)&#xD;
II) Collection of ʾarke-hymns (incipit fol. 55ra)&#xD;
- Hymns for Ḫǝdar&#xD;
- Hymns for Taḫśaś&#xD;
&#xD;
Additiones 1-5.</summary>
